  "detailed_description": "Bedroom Battlegrounds takes players into a vibrant and imaginative world, where a simple bedroom becomes the setting for epic turn-based battles. Lead your army of toy soldiers and vehicles against foes, maneuvering across a diverse battlefield of beds, desks, and toy boxes.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/882260a9b0d6b04e6307e221543ab873.poster.avif?t=1733575652\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/882260a9b0d6b04e6307e221543ab873.webm?t=1733575652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/882260a9b0d6b04e6307e221543ab873.mp4?t=1733575652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use strategy and wit to overcome enemies, taking advantage of the unique terrain that each room provides. Whether hiding behind a stack of books for cover or climbing up a toy castle for a vantage point, every move counts in this intricate game of strategy.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/93ed1e35c8e42f1184562fd34886ca74.poster.avif?t=1733575652\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/93ed1e35c8e42f1184562fd34886ca74.webm?t=1733575652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/93ed1e35c8e42f1184562fd34886ca74.mp4?t=1733575652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Welcome to Bedroom Battlegrounds - where the imagination comes alive, and childhood games turn into grand strategies!<br><br>At your disposal, you have a wide range of units, each with their own set of characteristics and abilities.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/60c927b418ae2b05569b9bedc8152aee.poster.avif?t=1733575652\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/60c927b418ae2b05569b9bedc8152aee.webm?t=1733575652\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2776110/extras/60c927b418ae2b05569b9bedc8152aee.mp4?t=1733575652\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Infantry:</h2>Cheap and versatile units, creating the core of your army.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vehicles:</h2>Fast and armoured, able to move your troops around the battlefield in a blink of an eye and deal heavy damage.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buildings:</h2>Supporting your units and protecting your home ground.<br><br>What's your plan to outsmart your opponents and become a champion of the battlegrounds?",
